title: Final Fantasy XIV - Before Meteor
description:
Before Meteor

----

Before Meteor: FINAL FANTASY XIV Original Soundtrack is the official soundtrack for the original release of Final Fantasy XIV, and includes all original songs composed by Nobuo Uematsu for the initial release, as well as every song added on subsequent patches and a remastered version of the "A New Beginning" trailer that was revealed once the Final Fantasy XIV servers were brought down.
